import { Avatar, Box, Button, Container, Grid, Paper, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'

export default function Login() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Grid container>
                <Grid item xs={4}>
                    <Paper>
                        <Avatar style={{margin: "0 auto"}}>

                        </Avatar>
                        <Box>
                            <TextField></TextField>
                            <TextField></TextField>
                            <Button color='primary'></Button>
                        </Box>

                        
                    </Paper>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
        
    )
}
